(24, 1, 7, 3, 'Samsung Front Load Washing Machine', 'Samsung washing machines span a range of models, from top-loading to front-loading, typically featuring digital inverter technology for energy efficiency and quiet operation, and often incorporating features like steam cleaning, self-cleaning cycles, and multiple wash programs tailored to various fabric types.  Many models include smart technology, such as Wi-Fi connectivity for remote control and monitoring, and utilize innovative washing technologies like AquaJet or SuperSpeed to enhance cleaning performance and reduce wash times. 1  They offer varying drum capacities, spin speeds, and energy efficiency ratings to cater to diverse laundry needs', '<p>Here are the full specifications for some of the latest <strong>Samsung washing machines</strong>, including the <strong>Samsung WW12CGP44DSH/TC 12kg Front Load Washer</strong> and the <strong>Samsung Bespoke AI Laundry Combo</strong>:</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Samsung WW12CGP44DSH/TC 12kg Front Load Washer</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Capacity</strong>: 12 kg</li>\r\n<li><strong>Type</strong>: Front Load</li>\r\n<li><strong>Inverter Technology</strong>: Yes (Energy-efficient motor for quieter operation)</li>\r\n<li><strong>Bubble Soak &amp; Bubble Shot Technology</strong>: Helps remove tough stains by penetrating detergent deep into the fabric</li>\r\n<li><strong>EcoBubble Technology</strong>: Creates bubbles to clean clothes effectively at lower temperatures</li>\r\n<li><strong>AI Control</strong>: Smart washing with personalized settings</li>\r\n<li><strong>Hygiene Steam Cycle</strong>: Eliminates bacteria and allergens</li>\r\n<li><strong>Drum Clean+</strong>: Keeps the drum fresh without using harsh chemicals</li>\r\n<li><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong>: High rating for reduced power consumption</li>\r\n<li><strong>Connectivity</strong>: SmartThings app support for remote control</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Samsung Bespoke AI Laundry Combo</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Washer &amp; Dryer Combo</strong>: No need to transfer laundry between machines</li>\r\n<li><strong>Bubble Shot Technology</strong>: Sprays soapy water into clothes for better detergent penetration</li>\r\n<li><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong>: 20% better than Class A standard</li>\r\n<li><strong>Heat Pump Drying</strong>: Ensures gentle drying at lower temperatures to prevent shrinkage</li>\r\n<li><strong>Smart Display</strong>: 7-inch touchscreen for controlling wash cycles and smart home integration</li>\r\n<li><strong>AI-powered Features</strong>: Bixby voice assistant for easy control, AI Energy Mode for power savings</li>\r\n<li><strong>SmartThings Integration</strong>: Remote control via Samsung’s SmartThings app</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Samsung also launched the <strong>Bespoke AI Washer</strong>, which is 55% more energy efficient than standard Class A washers. It includes <strong>Ecobubble and AI algorithms</strong> for intelligent washing adjustments (<a href=\"https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-bespoke-ai-washing-machines-dishwasher-launched-ifa-2024/\" target=\"_self\">Samsung launches new Bespoke AI dishwasher, washing machines - SamMobile</a>).</p>\r\n<p>For more details, you can check out Samsung\'s official website or retail listings (<a href=\"https://ansons.ph/product/samsung-ww12cgp44dsh-tc-12kg-front-load-washing-machine-2024/\" target=\"_self\">Samsung WW12CGP44DSH/TC 12kg. Front Load Washing Machine - 2024 - Ansons</a>). Let me know if you need specifications for any specific model!</p>\r\n', 1200, '10019', 'Active');

