(2, 2, 'Tommy', 'I’ve had airpods for several years now. I originally bought them when they first came out. I enjoyed them. I used them often, and they’ve always been great at the gym, on a walk, at work, or around the house with both of them in so I don’t hear my kids and husband every second.', '2025-03-12 01:46:50'),
